Troubleshooting:
check if the firewall is online - sudo ufw status verbose or sudo systemctl status ufw
reload firewall refresh changes if needed - sudo ufw reload
Check if the sshd is online - sudo systemctl status ssh or sudo systemctl status sshd
Network Configuration commands - nmcli connection show, nmcli device status, sudo systemctl restart NetworkManager
Security Considerations:
Check the open ports on the Linux server - sudo ss -tupln

